```plantuml
@startuml CMU-RERC-APT_tiramisu3-pr

actor User

participant "Mobile App\n(Ionic & Angular)" as MobileApp
participant "Java Frontend" as JavaFrontend
participant "Backend Data\nProcessor" as BackendProcessor
participant "AWS SQS" as AWSSQS
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "PostgresDB" as PostgresDB
participant "Python Predictor" as PythonPredictor

User -> MobileApp: Open App

note over MobileApp
  App Initialization:
  - Register Push Notifications
  - Initialize Alarms
  - Monitor Network
end note

MobileApp -> JavaFrontend: Request Real-time Data
JavaFrontend -> DynamoDB: Query Transit Data
DynamoDB --> JavaFrontend: Return Transit Data
JavaFrontend -> MobileApp: Send Real-time Data

User -> MobileApp: Set Favorite Route
MobileApp -> JavaFrontend: Write Favorite Route
JavaFrontend -> PostgresDB: Log Favorite Route
PostgresDB --> JavaFrontend: Acknowledge Logging

User -> MobileApp: Set Alarm
MobileApp -> JavaFrontend: Configure Alarm
JavaFrontend -> PostgresDB: Log Alarm Configuration
PostgresDB --> JavaFrontend: Acknowledge Logging

MobileApp -> AWSSQS: Send Alarm Configuration
AWSSQS -> BackendProcessor: Deliver Configuration

BackendProcessor -> DynamoDB: Read Current Transit Data
BackendProcessor -> PythonPredictor: Predict Route
PythonPredictor --> BackendProcessor: Return Prediction

BackendProcessor -> AWSSQS: Notify Predictions
AWSSQS -> MobileApp: Trigger Alarm Notification
MobileApp -> User: Display Notification

User -> MobileApp: Interact with Map
MobileApp -> JavaFrontend: Fetch Route Details
JavaFrontend -> DynamoDB: Retrieve Route Information
DynamoDB --> JavaFrontend: Return Route Information
JavaFrontend -> MobileApp: Send Route Details

@enduml
```